Description: To verfy validation message appears "Login Id  is not available in request" when LOGIN_ID not provided
To verify validation messsage appears "Password is not available in request" when password is not provided
To verify validation message appears "User does not exists in the system" when wrong LOGIN_ID provided
To verify validation message appears "User ID or Password is incorrect" when wrong PASSWORD provided
To verify validation message appears "Action type does not exists in the request" when TYPE is not provided
To verify validation message appears "username.is.required" when loginid  not provided
To verify validation message appears "category.is.required" when no of records not provided
To verify validation message appears "schedule.recharge.domain.is.required" when domain is not provided
To verify validation message appears "schedule.recharge.geodomain.is.required" when geo grphical domain  not provided
To verify all field validation messages appears when do not provide any value
To verify validation message appears "invalid.geographical.domain.code" when provide invalid geo graphical domain
To verify validation message appears "invalid.domain.code" when provide invalid domain code
To verify validation message appears "invalid.login.id" when provide invalid login id
To verify validation message appears "invalid.category.code" when provide invalid category code

To verfiy validation message appears "restrictedsubs.viewsingletrfschedule.msg.invalidmsisdn" if invalid mobile number is provided like minimum length of msisdn doesnot match to length defined in system preference
To verify validation message appears "restrictedsubs.viewsingletrfschedule.msg.nonetworkprefix" if no such network prefix is defined in system for which mobile number is entered.
To verify validation message appears "restrictedsubs.viewsingletrfschedule.msg.nonetworksupportmsisdn" if  network prefix of entered msisdn is different from network for which login id is entered.
To verify validation message appears "restrictedsubs.viewsingletrfschedule.msg.noschedule" if no scheduled data is found for entered details
To verify validation message appears "User ID or Password is incorrect" when wrong user details is provided to which role is not assigned
To verify validation message appears "msisdn.is.not.valid" when provide invalid msisdn like albhabets or special characters in msisdn field
To verify validation message appears "msisdn.is.not.valid" when provide msisdn is inserted of length more than max length specified in system preferences i.e. length 15
To verify validation message appears "schedule.recharge.username.is.not.valid" when provide invalid loginid  i.e. except alphanumeric and space in login id field
